{"tid":2029160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【文革2.0】報道指考評局「跪低」決定DQ日本侵華試題 參考其餘題目調分","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T08:10:56.000Z","uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5ec44591626c53babdde2f5dab7e11055c2b13","tid":2029160,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200522/large/1590121559_5e4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200522%2Flarge%2F1590121559_5e4b.jpg&h=cc52b8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教育局以「傷害民族感情」為由，越權要求考評局取消文憑試歷史科涉及「日本侵華」題目。《星島日報》今日引述消息獨家報道，指考評局委員會昨日再次開特別會議，已經決定取消題目，考評局日內作正式公佈；報道指，有關題目不會評卷及計算成績，改為參考其餘題目分數作調整。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200522/B2HRQRYEVHQ7DGCFHQEMFA7YIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2FB2HRQRYEVHQ7DGCFHQEMFA7YIU%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=e1e42a73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2FB2HRQRYEVHQ7DGCFHQEMFA7YIU%2F&h=45e6a5d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200522/B2HRQRYEVHQ7DGCFHQEMFA7YIU/</a>"},{"pid":"cd4edfcdf4f20ae5a6b8f04b4bf188f98fdc113f","tid":2029160,"uid":146288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b874f293fdbf6035cd24b39036baa610f1b60b9","tid":2029160,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"跪啦 邊有得唔跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdc985a192ea06c116cb32d18bf87d4827a5f7a","tid":2029160,"uid":146288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"學術自由冇㗎啦"},{"pid":"e083a1cdcd347d6e98a8c2b243be973da229075d","tid":2029160,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sc